    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>God&apos;s Remedy for Selfishness and Covetousness</strong>&mdash;The giving that is the fruit of self-denial is a wonderful help to the giver. It imparts an education that enables us more fully to comprehend the work of Him who went about doing good, relieving the suffering, and supplying the needs of the destitute.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">11<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"YI 9-10-1907.5\" data-link=\"469.5612\">The Youth&apos;s Instructor, September 10, 1907</span>.</span></a></sup>",
